  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Select one spell. You cast that spell with greater than normal power.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Int 13, Spell Focus.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Select one spell of a school for which you have taken the Spell Focus feat. Treat your caster level as being two higher for all level-variable effects of the spell.<br/><br/> Every time you gain an even level in the spellcasting class you chose your spell from, you can choose a new spell to replace the spell selected with this feat, and that spell becomes your specialized spell.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>You can gain this feat multiple times. Its effects do not stack. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a different spell.",
